[SPEAKER_11]: It has to be a decision that they make and they have to apply to convert to non-student housing.

153
00:23:13,970 --> 00:23:15,551
[SPEAKER_11]: And if they change the title,

154
00:23:17,283 --> 00:23:18,484
[SPEAKER_11]: that that would be part of it.

155
00:23:19,365 --> 00:23:26,412
[SPEAKER_11]: A change in more than 20 percent of the ownership entity could happen, or if the lease was assigned to another entity.

156
00:23:27,473 --> 00:23:40,665
[SPEAKER_11]: There would be a hearing at the CDB where there would be material compliance with the approved operation and management plan, or that these are the reasons why it might convert, or that the property no longer meets the definition of purpose

