00:30:33,870 --> 00:30:37,032
[SPEAKER_11]: I'd have to triple check that, but we're not recommending to allow it.

224
00:30:37,112 --> 00:30:38,714
[SPEAKER_11]: So we don't think it really needs to be

225
00:30:39,374 --> 00:30:43,838
