1307
02:06:41,992 --> 02:06:45,633
[SPEAKER_27]: They understand that there's a process in place that we know that needs some change.

1308
02:06:46,234 --> 02:06:51,976
[SPEAKER_27]: So I mean, what I keep getting back on my end are different studies.

1309
02:06:51,996 --> 02:07:03,800
[SPEAKER_27]: I know that we talked about traffic studies in the past, but in this quarter, especially, understanding the traffic studies, understanding the density issues, understanding the setbacks.

1310
02:07:03,820 --> 02:07:09,302
