1311
02:07:10,368 --> 02:07:16,773
[SPEAKER_27]: evident are the height restrictions and the heights of what we're looking at for this corridor.

1312
02:07:16,813 --> 02:07:31,344
[SPEAKER_27]: But I too want to caution everyone or express the feelings that I'm sharing from the residents that have reached out to me that this is hopefully a process that

1313
02:07:32,940 --> 02:07:42,344
[SPEAKER_27]: isn't done tonight or move forward tonight because of a timeline, but maybe looking at it more of a totality and say, we want to get this right.

1314
02:07:42,784 --> 02:07:50,028
[SPEAKER_27]: And using the Meffitt Square piece as a partnership really showed why it could be successful.

1315
02:07:51,588 --> 02:07:53,629
