02:08:14,377 --> 02:08:16,758
[SPEAKER_27]: And this is a huge change for our community.

1320
02:08:16,798 --> 02:08:25,462
[SPEAKER_27]: And I too understand new growth is what's going to support our community financially.

1321
02:08:25,802 --> 02:08:28,503
[SPEAKER_27]: And it's something we haven't had in many, many years, but

1322
02:08:29,364 --> 02:08:52,749
[SPEAKER_27]: I just wanted to share after the comments that our residents presented in the multi text messaging and emails receiving that I promised that I would share their concerns of speed and height and neighborhood feel and making sure that that was expressed.

1323
